---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Sesje Feedbackowe"
  description="Umow sie na sesje feedbackowa z ekspertem CBT. Poznaj platforme AI Therapy Support na zywo i podziel sie swoimi uwagami."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-gray-950 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-sage-600/20 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-sage-600/20 text-sage-500 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Sesje Feedbackowe
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight">
          Sesja Feedbackowa z Ekspertem CBT
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Umow sie na sesje demonstracyjna. Pokażemy Ci platforme na zywo i odpowiemy na wszystkie pytania.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cal.com Embed -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-8 min-h-[600px]" id="cal-embed-container">
        <!-- Cal.com inline embed -->
        <div id="cal-inline" style="width:100%;height:100%;overflow:scroll;min-height:600px;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Info Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-sage-50 text-sage-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">30 minut</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Krotka, konkretna sesja dostosowana do Twoich potrzeb.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-sage-50 text-sage-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m15.75 10.5 4.72-4.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.28.53v11.38a.75.75 0 0 1-1.28.53l-4.72-4.72M4.5 18.75h9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25h-9A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 7.5v9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Online</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Spotkanie odbywa sie zdalnie — potrzebujesz tylko przegladarki.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-sage-50 text-sage-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.129.166 2.27.293 3.423.379.35.026.67.21.865.501L12 21l2.755-4.133a1.14 1.14 0 0 1 .865-.501 48.172 48.172 0 0 0 3.423-.379c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0 0 12 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Twoj Feedback</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sesja feedbackowa pomaga nam rozwijac platfome zgodnie z potrzebami terapeutow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

